* A 2014 Yamaha Baby Grand Piano
* A PlayStation 5
*   Apple Vision Pro
*   Meta Quest Oculus
* A Nintendo Switch OLED
* An Xbox Series S (512GB SSD)
* An iPad Air (5th generation, 256GB)
* Eric Clapton's 1939 Martin OOO-42 Guitar
* A Leica S (TyR 007) Digital SLR Camera
